{"tid":2076637,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罷食CP?","createTime":"2020-06-23T16:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T16:12:02.000Z","uid":115638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57518f97a8bf83e3214ce05c803ea756126d1e4e","tid":2076637,"uid":115638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xb88e4K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxb88e4K.jpg&h=524f1c4c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCP登頭版前，可能好多人都仲有買佢地啲野食，貪方便又好，話佢好食又好，但唔知有無人記得，大約6年前好多外國媒體都報導過嘅東南亞奴隸船問題，喺東南亞好多人俾人賣豬仔上泰國啲漁船，長期俾人虐待，船長隨便就可以行刑式處決奴隸，當時CP就俾人發現佢地就係同奴隸船買佢地啲漁獲。<br />\n<br />\n有關報導可以睇返：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2014/jun/10/supermarket-prawns-thailand-produced-slave-labour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fglobal-development%2F2014%2Fjun%2F10%2Fsupermarket-prawns-thailand-produced-slave-labour&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=91f801f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2014/jun/10/supermarket-prawns-thailand-produced-slave-labour</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20150727/c27seaslaves/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fasia-pacific%2F20150727%2Fc27seaslaves%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=cf7e128a\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20150727/c27seaslaves/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20140612/18755365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140612%2F18755365&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=d9034fbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140612%2F18755365&h=318bbbc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/internat